I have not been able to test the code below, but it should at least give you some direction. Please note that the micro:bit acts as a master. I don&#39;t think the micro:bit can act as a slave on a I2C bus (but I might be wrong here). Also note that you may have to change the path to the `microbit_zfp.gpr` in the project file.

**default.gpr**
```
